4 strength off the southwestern coast of  Mexico , the U.S.
Hurricane Center said in an advisory at about 4:40 p.m. East
Coast time.  Hilary, which had weakened to a Category 3 hurricane, has
top winds of 135 miles (217 kilometers) an hour. In the
